// SplitPane
// Resizable split-pane layout components using react-resizable-panels.
// SplitPane: two-panel with optional collapse support.
// ThreeWaySplitPane: three-panel with two resize handles, left and right
// panels collapsible independently.

FUNCTION SplitPane(primary, secondary, direction, defaultSize, collapsible, onSizeChange, ...) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Two-panel PanelGroup. Primary panel holds primaryPanelRef for
  programmatic collapse/expand.
  Drag handle between panels.
  Exposes collapsePrimary/expandPrimary methods via ref.

---

FUNCTION handleLayout(sizes) -> void
  Extracts primarySize from sizes[0].sizePercentage.
  Fires onSizeChange(primarySize).
  Detects collapse/expand transitions and updates collapsed state.

---

FUNCTION collapsePrimary() -> void
  Calls primaryPanelRef.current.collapse().

---

FUNCTION expandPrimary() -> void
  Calls primaryPanelRef.current.expand().

---

FUNCTION ThreeWaySplitPane(left, center, right, ...) -> JSX            EXPORT
  Three-panel PanelGroup with two resize handles.
  Left and right panels are independently collapsible.
  Handles layout change to track each panel's collapsed state.
